## Limits

| Limit | Value |
|---|---|
| Max output resolution | {/* e.g. 2048x2048 */} |
| Max images per call (`n`) | {/* e.g. 4 */} |
| Supports init image (img2img) | {/* Yes / No */} |
| Supports negative prompt | {/* Yes / No */} |
| Supports seed reproduction | {/* Yes / No */} |
| Sync? | Yes (≤30s typical) |
| Avg latency for 1024² | {/* e.g. 6-8s */} |
